otp/verify
This service is used by the developer to verify an OTP entered by a subscriber into the application. Upon a successful verification the subscription process of AppLink will be activated.

Note: The OTP dispatched to the subscriber by triggering this API is only valid for 5 minutes

Verify OTP
Request Body schema: application/json;charset=utf-8
applicationId
required
string
Used to identify the application. This is a unique identifier generated while provisioning an application.

Only a single value can be sent per request.

password
required
string
This API key will be sent to your registered email address on the platform upon application approval.

referenceNo
required
string
Reference number returned with request OTP API

See request OTP API response for more information

otp
required
string
One time password (OTP) to be used for MSISDN verification for the application

Responses
